lyrics:
[Verse]
Racing through the city, I'm on a mission
Bass and drums pumpin', my heart's ignition
Spittin' lyrics fast, ain't no time for hesitation
Feelin' the energy, embracing elevation

[Chorus]
Fast-paced vibes, keep the tempo high
Bass dropping hard, feel it deep inside
Drums beating strong, they amplify
In this rap flow, we're gonna fly
